Create AWS account

Provision one server manually

Install terraform
   1. sudo yum install -y yum-utils
   2. sudo yum-config-manager --add-repo https://rpm.releases.hashicorp.com/AmazonLinux/hashicorp.repo
   3. sudo yum -y install terraform
   4. terraform init
   5. create providers.tf, vaeriables.tf and webserver.tf
   6. terraform plan
   7. Terraform apply 
      --> You need to approve manually by entering "Yes" or you can use Terraform apply â€“auto-approv
   
Install ansible
   1. wget https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm
   2. yum install epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm
   3. yum install git python python-devel python-pip openssl ansible -y
